sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户程序
    participant libcudart as libcudart
    participant libcuda as libcuda (Driver)
    participant GPU as GPU

    Note over User,GPU: 普通 launch
    User->>libcudart: vec_add<<<>>>(args)
    libcudart->>libcuda: cuLaunchKernel()
    libcuda->>GPU: ioctl(0x4e, cmd_buf)
    Note over User,GPU: cudaDeviceSynchronize
    libcuda->>GPU: ioctl(0x2b, fence)

    Note over User,GPU: Graph 捕获
    User->>libcudart: cudaStreamBeginCapture(stream)
    User->>libcudart: vec_add<<<>>>(args) [captured]
    User->>libcudart: vec_mul<<<>>>(args) [captured]
    User->>libcudart: cudaStreamEndCapture() → graph

    Note over User,GPU: Graph 实例化 (进程内 JIT)
    libcudart->>libcuda: cudaGraphInstantiate()
    libcuda->>libcuda: dlopen + NVVM JIT
    libcuda-->>libcudart: graph_exec

    Note over User,GPU: Graph launch
    User->>libcudart: cudaGraphLaunch(graph_exec)
    libcudart->>libcuda: cuGraphLaunch()
    libcuda->>GPU: ioctl(0x4e, cmd_buf)
    Note right of GPU: 与普通 launch<br/>相同的 ioctl
